1) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-1. Group of four Mr Leslie Faber Mr Mark Kinghorne Mr Charles Fulton sitting at table, Mr George Alexander standing with his right hand on Mr Kinghorne's shoulder'. 4cm x 4cm.

2) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 10" x 8" size, No 42303-2. Group of five, Mr George Alexander and lady sitting on stone seat, Mr Mark Kinghorne leaning over back of seat, Mr Fulton standing and Mr Leslie Faber sitting in chair at left of picture'. 3cm x 4cm.

3) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-3. Group of five, Mr George Alexander bowing over head of gentleman in centre, Mr Leslie Faber standing at right holding sword, Mr Kinghorne and Mr Fulton standing together at left of picture'. 4cm x 4cm.

4) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-5. Group of two Miss Lilian Braithwaite sitting on stone seat, Mr Alexander standing handing her a small bow of ribbon'. 4cm x 3cm.

5) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-6. Group of five, Mr George Alexander and Mr Herbert Dansey fencing, Mr Kinghorne standing in centre resting right foot on seat by tree, Mr Leslie Faber standing at right, Mr Fulton standing at left'. 4cm x 4cm.

6) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-7. Group of five, Mr George Alexander and Mr Herbert Dansey fencing, Mr Kinghorne standing in centre, Mr Fulton standing near him and Mr Leslie Faber standing at right of picture'. 4cm x 4cm.

7) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-8. Group [of] Mr George Alexander in centre with left knee on chair and left hand on table, Mr Leslie Faber and Mr Charles Fulton sitting the other side of table, Mr Kinghorne holding notes in hand sitting at left'. 4cm x 4cm.

8) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-9. Group [of] Mr George Alexander in centre with right knee on chair, Mr Leslie Faber, Mr Mark Kinghorne and Mr Charles Fulton sitting at table at right watching him'. 4cm x 4cm.

9) 'Photograph of 'The Garden of Lies' 12" x 10" size, No 42303-10. Group [of] Mr Mark Kinghorne, Mr Leslie Faber, Mr Charles Fulton sitting at table, Mr George Alexander standing by, Mr Faber offering his hand to Mr Fulton'. 4cm x 4cm.
